        "id": 5631
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-04-08T12:42:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I haven\u0027t come up with a scenario yet (because setting fDeclared seems to guard it), but not (being able to) copy fDeclaration feels like something that might bite us in the future?",
